    "case.realface.benefits.desc": "<ul><li><b>Peace of mind</b> ‚Äî instant verification reduces anxiety (\"Is this person real?\").</li><li><b>Confidence in authenticity</b> ‚Äî green light means high probability the person is genuine (not invented or impersonated).</li><li><b>Time & money protection</b> ‚Äî early red flags prevent prolonged chats with fakes, avoiding emotional manipulation and financial requests.</li><li><b>Proactive safety</b> ‚Äî users can verify suspicious profiles before investing emotionally or sending money/videos.</li></ul>",

